### ECL API Examples
### Make sure server is running: uvicorn src.ecl.server.app:app --reload

### Basic verification request
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Is Knysna in the Western Cape of South Africa?",
  "models": ["stub:gpt", "stub:claude"]
}

###

### Question with multiple claims
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Paris is the capital of France. It has a population of over 2 million people.",
  "models": ["stub:gpt", "stub:claude", "stub:gemini"]
}

###

### Single model verification
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "The Earth orbits around the Sun?",
  "models": ["stub:gpt"]
}